  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Gain 2 clotheing items from the shop before each encounter. One clothing
    item can be worn on  each the head, torso, legs, and feet. Each item has a unique
    ability that triggers after its step counter reaches 0.

    During an encounter,
    you will fight enemies whose abilties also rely on step counters. Every few seconds,
    all step counters are decreased, and any at 0 have their ability trigger.

    Player
    abilities trigger first from head to toe. Then monster abilties trigger left
    to right. If an ability goes to 0 steps after it is passed, it will be triggered
    regardless. Once an ability is triggered, its step counter resets.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5ad6beea3a8503c4b850bbb6baa5974b, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 1197442766912020547, guid: 5ad6beea3a8503c4b850bbb6baa5974b, type: 2}
